high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the tomato off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside, then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave, take the tomato out and close the door.
Turn around and towards the door, then hang a right and walk across the room to the sink.
Put the heated tomato in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Move to the island to the right of you
pick up a tomato from the island
move to the microwave ahead of you
heat the tomato with the microwave
move to the sink to the left of you
put the tomato inside the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn and move to the far end of the kitchen island, so you're facing the tomato and fork.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Carry the tomato around the island to the microwave on the counter parallel to the island.
Place the tomato in the microwave, turn it on, and then remove the tomato once heated.
Carry the tomato across the kitchen to the sink.
Place the tomato in the right side of the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in the kitchen sink.
